data.description: This 4 bedroom, 2 full bathroom ranch over a full walk-out basement is one that you do not want to miss! Situated on a gorgeous 1 acre lot in the heart of Unionville, this home has so much to offer. The kitchen was freshly updated in May of 2023 featuring new vinyl plank flooring, countertops, sink and faucet, dishwasher and range. New vinyl plank flooring was laid throughout the home as well as new carpet in bedrooms and basement in May of ‘23. The prime location of this property gives you the best of both worlds; relax and enjoy the peace and quiet of the country feel but make it to all the East side of Bloomington has to offer in just 10 minutes. This property is hard to beat!
